n.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Y%C3%AAm/author-V2PfiYxdyB2eEu42wOrwSw">Phạm Trọng Yêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C3%94-th%C3%AA-kh%C3%BAc/poem-K7Y8BGaymd_0bZQCaZbdUQ">Ô thê khúc - 烏棲曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Ki%C3%AAn-Ng%C3%B4/Th%C3%A2u-trang-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-v4NM9X-kqBGJn_Copa6nmQ">Thâu trang từ - 收妝詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Ki%C3%AAn-Ng%C3%B4/author-qmxkUt-i7s_YdIHj1-szkw">Thi Kiên Ngô</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Giang-%C4%91%C3%A0i-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-%C4%91%C3%A0i-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-3wHO79-LwQUbFXKcTwMUrg">Vọng Giang đài, đắc đài tự - 望江臺得臺字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
